doc-+do
doc-u+do
doc-bounds
doc--[do
doc-u-[do
doc--do
doc-u-do
doc-array>mem
doc-mem+do
doc-mem-do
doc-do
doc-for
doc-loop
doc-+loop
doc--loop
doc-next
doc-i
doc-j
doc-k
doc-i'
doc-delta-i
doc-leave
doc-?leave
doc-unloop
